BERIKAN SAYA BIR SEJUK ITU CEPAT

00:57:25.709 --> 00:57:27.244
MENGULUK

00:57:27.311 --> 00:57:28.312
WISKI JIMIN

00:57:28.378 --> 00:57:29.446
[dalam Bahasa Inggeris] Terima kasih.

00:57:29.513 --> 00:57:31.114
BIR DRAF JUNG KOOK

00:57:31.848 --> 00:57:34.318
SORAK

00:57:34.384 --> 00:57:36.453
Bir ini...

00:57:36.520 --> 00:57:37.521
besar.

00:57:40.023 --> 00:57:42.459
TEKAK TERBUKA SEPENUHNYA

00:57:44.861 --> 00:57:46.863
Bir sememangnya yang terbaik.

00:57:48.732 --> 00:57:49.800
[dalam bahasa Korea] Yang ini...

00:57:51.234 --> 00:57:54.371
Oleh kerana ia mempunyai unsur Swiss dalam namanya,
saya rasa ia adalah wiski Swiss.

00:57:54.438 --> 00:57:55.706
Biar saya cuba.

00:57:58.709 --> 00:57:59.977
Baunya sungguh manis.

00:58:01.378 --> 00:58:03.347
Memang betul. Awak betul.

00:58:04.348 --> 00:58:05.716
SORAK...

00:58:05.782 --> 00:58:08.051
Apa itu lagi? Santé?

00:58:08.552 --> 00:58:09.553
Kesihatan.

00:58:10.387 --> 00:58:12.756
MENCUBA WISKI SWISS DI SWITZERLAND

00:58:15.559 --> 00:58:16.560
[mengeluh]

00:58:16.626 --> 00:58:19.363
Rasanya sangat seronok
dapat keluar minum macam ni.

00:58:20.097 --> 00:58:23.467
-Betul ke?
-Hanya duduk di sini, berehat.

00:58:27.037 --> 00:58:28.739
Ia benar-benar sebuah pekan kecil yang sangat menyeronokkan.

00:58:30.240 --> 00:58:31.475
Ya.

00:58:33.610 --> 00:58:35.912
TEMPAT YANG BERTAHAN

00:58:35.979 --> 00:58:38.715
KEHIDUPAN DAN KEDAMAIAN

00:58:39.583 --> 00:58:41.551
MENEMUI PESONA

00:58:41.618 --> 00:58:44.654
ZERMATT PADA WAKTU MALAM

00:58:47.991 --> 00:58:49.659
[Jung Kook] Kentang goreng ini sangat sedap.

00:58:49.993 --> 00:58:52.963
Kentang Goreng Swiss di Lorongnya

00:59:00.971 --> 00:59:03.006
JEDA

00:59:05.308 --> 00:59:06.309
MAIN

00:59:07.477 --> 00:59:08.879
JEDA LAGI

00:59:08.945 --> 00:59:11.148
TENTERA SWISS MUNCUL

00:59:11.214 --> 00:59:13.116
MELAMPAI SALAM KEPADA TENTERA

00:59:13.183 --> 00:59:16.787
PERTEMUAN YANG TIDAK DIJANGKA
DENGAN SEORANG GADIS TENTERA SWISS

00:59:16.853 --> 00:59:17.854
Macam mana dia tahu?

00:59:18.955 --> 00:59:19.956
Dia menangis.

00:59:22.159 --> 00:59:24.828
SEORANG GADIS TENTERA YANG MENGAIRKAN RASA
AKIBAT PERTEMUAN YANG MENGECIL

00:59:25.629 --> 00:59:27.197
SELAMAT TINGGAL, GADIS TENTERA

00:59:27.264 --> 00:59:28.432
Dia comel.

00:59:28.498 --> 00:59:31.134
PERTEMUAN YANG RINGKAS TETAPI MENYENTUH HATI

00:59:31.701 --> 00:59:34.471
DETIK YANG TIDAK AKAN DILUPAKAN OLEH GADIS TENTERA

00:59:35.472 --> 00:59:37.374
DAN SATU DETIK YANG TIDAK AKAN KAMI LUPAKAN

00:59:37.441 --> 00:59:41.711
SETEGUH BIR YANG MENYEGARKAN

00:59:41.778 --> 00:59:46.049
SETEGUH WISKI PAHIT MANIS

00:59:46.116 --> 00:59:47.851
Matahari terbenam.

00:59:49.553 --> 00:59:50.954
Betul, hampir.

00:59:52.355 --> 00:59:54.825
-Awak tahu...
-Rasanya macam waktu malam sekarang.

00:59:56.159 --> 00:59:58.962
KEGELAPAN PERLAHAN-LAHAN TURUN

01:00:00.297 --> 01:00:05.068
KETENANGAN MENYEBAR DI KAMPUNG

01:00:06.703 --> 01:00:09.906
[Jung Kook] Sungguh indah pada waktu malam.
Awak cuma mahu duduk diam.

01:00:09.973 --> 01:00:14.511
Sejujurnya, saya teringin sangat nak minum
dengan awak dekat sini.

01:00:14.578 --> 01:00:17.647
Kerana, di Korea,
kita tidak pernah mendapat peluang seperti ini.

01:00:17.714 --> 01:00:20.283
INGIN MENIKMATI DETIK LUAR YANG PERLAHAN

01:00:21.084 --> 01:00:23.386
DAN MALAM INI

01:00:23.453 --> 01:00:25.822
MEREKA SEDANG MENIKMATI KEBEBASAN DI ZERMATT

01:00:25.889 --> 01:00:27.224
[Jung Kook berdengung]

01:00:27.290 --> 01:00:28.859
Awak cuma minum yang tu je ke?

01:00:28.925 --> 01:00:30.393
Ya, ini gelas keempat saya.

01:00:33.697 --> 01:00:35.465
Lepas yang ni, jom kita balik.

01:00:35.532 --> 01:00:37.501
-Ya.
-Kita kena bangun awal esok.

01:00:40.203 --> 01:00:44.107
Nampaknya kebanyakan tempat
dibuka sehingga tengah malam.

01:00:44.174 --> 01:00:46.977
Saya rasa tempat ini mempunyai paling ramai pelancong.

01:00:47.477 --> 01:00:48.745
Ia meriah.

01:00:50.881 --> 01:00:52.516
[Jimin] Ya Tuhan, saya suka ini.

01:00:53.750 --> 01:00:58.855
Awak kata awak nak tinggal
di Switzerland, kan? Sekurang-kurangnya untuk seketika.

01:00:58.922 --> 01:01:01.358
Adakah ia di sini atau di tempat lain?

01:01:01.424 --> 01:01:03.426
Tempat yang paling sesuai dengan citarasa saya.

01:01:04.661 --> 01:01:07.797
Saya suka tempat yang paling mencolok mata dan paling meriah.

01:01:08.498 --> 01:01:11.034
-Suka bandar macam ni?
-Ya, betul sekali.

01:01:11.101 --> 01:01:13.103
Ia bagus. Sangat bagus.

01:01:14.237 --> 01:01:17.974
ZERMATT, SEBUAH BANDAR YANG MENCURI HATI MEREKA

01:01:18.041 --> 01:01:21.678
Kami melakukan banyak perkara yang menyeronokkan
di Zermatt ini.

01:01:21.745 --> 01:01:24.214
Jika kita pergi bermain ski esok,
ia akan menjadi perlawanan akhir yang sempurna.

01:01:24.281 --> 01:01:25.282
Bermain ski.

01:01:25.348 --> 01:01:27.450
Harap-harap saya tak sakit-sakit badan bila bangun tidur nanti.

01:01:27.984 --> 01:01:29.386
Beritahu saya jika ya, okay?

01:01:30.887 --> 01:01:31.955
SAKITNYA

01:01:32.022 --> 01:01:33.924
Jika ya, mari kita pergi bermain kereta luncur salji.

01:01:33.990 --> 01:01:36.059
Meluncur salji kedengaran menyeronokkan juga.

01:01:36.126 --> 01:01:39.262
Kita cuma boleh ambil beg plastik
dan meluncur ke bawah.

01:01:39.329 --> 01:01:40.697
Beritahu saya jika ia sakit.

01:01:41.298 --> 01:01:42.732
Saya salah pasang.

01:01:43.233 --> 01:01:44.568
Saya akan kupas yang ini.

01:01:45.535 --> 01:01:50.006
Awak tahu tak, saya hampir tidak pernah memakai pembalut
apabila saya cedera.

01:01:50.073 --> 01:01:52.108
-Tapi...
-Saya akan tanggalkannya dalam sehari.

01:01:52.175 --> 01:01:54.444
Aku tak kisah pun kalau ia meninggalkan parut.

01:01:54.511 --> 01:01:56.379
-Saya juga macam tu.
-Betul.

01:01:56.446 --> 01:01:59.649
Tapi ia bukan tentang saya. Ia tentang awak.
Awak macam adik saya.

01:01:59.716 --> 01:02:01.251
Jadi saya lebih suka awak tak buat.

01:02:01.318 --> 01:02:02.819
Namun, ia tetap satu kenangan, tahu tak?

01:02:02.886 --> 01:02:05.021
-Tidak juga.
-Tentang masa awak cedera.

01:02:05.088 --> 01:02:06.823
PARUT = KENANGAN

01:02:06.890 --> 01:02:09.859
Macam ni?
Tiga jahitan yang saya dapat dalam tentera?

01:02:09.926 --> 01:02:11.661
Saya juga ada beberapa parut dari situ.

01:02:12.195 --> 01:02:13.296
Kehidupan tentera.

01:02:13.363 --> 01:02:16.299
Korang mungkin tak tahu ni,
tapi Jung Kook ada dua parut di sini.

01:02:16.366 --> 01:02:19.970
Dan saya ada tiga...
Tidak, empat titik kecil di sini.

01:02:20.904 --> 01:02:22.439
Saya tidak banyak berfikir.

01:02:22.505 --> 01:02:25.942
Dulu masa saya dapat yang besar pertama saya,

01:02:26.009 --> 01:02:29.379
Saya langsung tidak sedar apa yang saya sedang lakukan.
Ia sangat meletihkan, jadi...

01:02:29.446 --> 01:02:31.615
-Ia sangat berat, saya tidak dapat mengangkatnya.
-Ya.

01:02:31.681 --> 01:02:34.184
Saya sangat letih,
jadi semasa saya memegang penyodok itu,

01:02:34.784 --> 01:02:35.785
Saya bersandar padanya.

01:02:35.852 --> 01:02:36.853
Oh!

01:02:36.920 --> 01:02:37.921
Awak hanya bersandar padanya.

01:02:37.988 --> 01:02:40.290
-Di atas periuk panas macam ni?
-Ya.

01:02:40.357 --> 01:02:43.760
Ya, saya memang mempercayainya.
Begitulah keadaannya.

01:02:44.361 --> 01:02:45.795
Ketika itulah saya mendapat parut itu.

01:02:46.329 --> 01:02:49.466
DENGAN ITU MENYIMPAK LEGENDA JUNG KOOK
TENTANG PARUT YANG GEMILANG

01:02:52.535 --> 01:02:58.241
Kali pertama saya suka seseorang

01:02:58.908 --> 01:03:02.879
yang bukan orang Korea
adalah ketika saya pergi ke AS

01:03:02.946 --> 01:03:04.748
untuk program pelatih selama sebulan itu.

01:03:04.814 --> 01:03:06.683
BANGUN?

01:03:06.750 --> 01:03:09.185
-Bukankah awak darjah 9 masa tu?
-Darjah 8.

01:03:09.252 --> 01:03:11.054
-Darjah 8?
-Ya.

01:03:11.121 --> 01:03:15.692
Ia adalah seorang gadis yang berada di sana
untuk kelas tarian seperti saya.

01:03:15.759 --> 01:03:18.995
Dia juga sangat muda.
Seorang pelajar seperti saya.

01:03:19.062 --> 01:03:21.598
Pada mulanya, saya sangkakan dia sangat cantik.

01:03:21.665 --> 01:03:23.466
HAHAH

01:03:23.533 --> 01:03:25.235
KISAH CINTA PERTAMA YANG MENARIK

01:03:25.302 --> 01:03:27.937
Tapi lepas tu saya mula
kerap berjumpa dengannya.

01:03:29.005 --> 01:03:30.373
Kemudian cikgu itu memberitahu saya,

01:03:30.907 --> 01:03:34.110
-"Pergi cakap dengan dia! Sekali sahaja."
-Betul ke?

01:03:35.812 --> 01:03:37.147
GEMBIRA DENGAN CERITA INI

01:03:37.213 --> 01:03:38.315
KECIL

01:03:38.381 --> 01:03:40.950
Tapi saya macam,
"Macam mana? Saya tak boleh bertutur dalam Bahasa Inggeris pun."

01:03:41.017 --> 01:03:42.452
Kami tidak dapat berkomunikasi.

01:03:43.019 --> 01:03:44.120
Tetapi jika sekarang?

01:03:44.187 --> 01:03:46.890
-Mungkin saya akan teruskan.
-Betul tak?

01:03:49.092 --> 01:03:50.226
[dalam Bahasa Inggeris] Saya suka awak.

01:03:50.760 --> 01:03:51.761
Saya suka awak.

01:03:54.964 --> 01:03:56.833
BUDAK MALU

01:03:56.900 --> 01:03:59.369
Itu sebenarnya cerita yang comel.

01:03:59.436 --> 01:04:01.371
-Tak perlu sunting.
-[dalam bahasa Korea] Ya.

01:04:01.438 --> 01:04:03.006
-Hanya dalam darjah 8.
-Saya masih muda.

01:04:03.073 --> 01:04:07.077
-Awak masih ingat dengan baik, kan?
-Sudah tentu.

01:04:07.143 --> 01:04:09.979
Seperti cinta yang tidak kesampaian.

01:04:10.046 --> 01:04:12.949
-"The Truth Untold."
-Yeah, "The Truth Untold."

01:04:13.016 --> 01:04:15.118
I couldn't even say a word.

01:04:16.619 --> 01:04:20.824
[singing]

01:04:20.890 --> 01:04:23.226
[both singing]

01:04:35.405 --> 01:04:38.675
IN BEAUTIFUL ZERMATT

01:04:38.742 --> 01:04:42.479
THEY REMINISCE ABOUT BEAUTIFUL MEMORIES

01:04:43.079 --> 01:04:47.751
You know how we sang "The Truth Untold"
back in the army karaoke?

01:04:47.817 --> 01:04:52.789
If we approach it the way we practiced
back then, it'll come out smoother.

01:04:52.856 --> 01:04:54.791
Honestly, that song...

01:04:55.458 --> 01:05:01.030
During BTS concerts, it always felt like
a bit of trauma for me.

01:05:01.097 --> 01:05:03.666
Even though we practiced together
in the military,

01:05:03.733 --> 01:05:06.536
I also had lessons after I got out.

01:05:06.603 --> 01:05:08.805
-Right.
-But there's one problem.

01:05:08.872 --> 01:05:10.540
-What?
-It's...

01:05:10.607 --> 01:05:12.542
It doesn't sound cool.

01:05:12.609 --> 01:05:13.610
Cool?

01:05:13.676 --> 01:05:18.581
Well, you can add that flair
after you get comfortable with it.

01:05:18.648 --> 01:05:20.150
At first, I was taken aback.

01:05:20.216 --> 01:05:22.886
Because you can't just add coolness

01:05:23.853 --> 01:05:27.857
-unless you've sung like that before.
-Right.

01:05:27.924 --> 01:05:31.661
-I'd never sung like that in 10 years.
-Yes. Right.

01:05:31.728 --> 01:05:33.863
Only now, after all that new training,

01:05:33.930 --> 01:05:36.533
I can finally sing
without hurting my throat.

01:05:37.333 --> 01:05:38.334
And...

01:05:40.069 --> 01:05:42.906
I think singing clean and simple
might sound better.

01:05:42.972 --> 01:05:46.910
I still take lessons with my teacher,
but I also have you, you know?

01:05:46.976 --> 01:05:48.645
I listen to how you sing,

01:05:49.512 --> 01:05:51.614
then think back to what I've learned.

01:05:51.681 --> 01:05:53.950
And I think there's this connection.

01:05:54.651 --> 01:05:56.453
What you say and what my teacher says

01:05:56.953 --> 01:05:58.521
are totally different,

01:05:58.588 --> 01:06:01.357
-Right.
-but when I hear you sing,

01:06:01.424 --> 01:06:03.793
it actually sounds pretty similar.

01:06:03.860 --> 01:06:05.195
Listening nearby...

01:06:05.728 --> 01:06:07.997
Anyway, I've realized one thing for sure.

01:06:09.098 --> 01:06:13.736
You have great strengths,
and we're totally different.

01:06:13.803 --> 01:06:16.072
I've learned that.

01:06:16.139 --> 01:06:21.644
And despite that,
since we've practiced together,

01:06:21.711 --> 01:06:23.646
all the advice you've given me

01:06:23.713 --> 01:06:27.350
has always helped me a lot.

01:06:27.917 --> 01:06:29.786
That's the most important part.

01:06:31.754 --> 01:06:32.755
Shall we go?

01:06:33.256 --> 01:06:35.692
-Let's go.
-Yeah, let's go. I'll go pay.

01:06:36.226 --> 01:06:37.494
You're paying, right?

01:06:38.661 --> 01:06:40.396
Give us one chance a day.

01:06:40.463 --> 01:06:41.831
One card-swipe chance.

01:06:41.898 --> 01:06:44.634
For the director and all the staff, too.

01:06:44.701 --> 01:06:46.603
Whatever it is, just once.

01:06:46.669 --> 01:06:47.670
Jimin Chance?

01:06:48.872 --> 01:06:50.073
You want anything?

01:06:50.139 --> 01:06:51.140
JIMIN CHANCE DAY

01:06:51.207 --> 01:06:52.208
You already ordered?

01:06:52.275 --> 01:06:54.244
JIMIN MADE SURE THE STAFF GOT THEIR MEALS

01:06:54.310 --> 01:06:55.745
Okay.

01:06:55.812 --> 01:06:56.813
Sounds good.

01:06:56.880 --> 01:06:59.782
Honestly, I was so tired today.
I didn't want to come out.

01:06:59.849 --> 01:07:04.020
But I did because I wanted to grab
some beer with all the staff.

01:07:04.087 --> 01:07:06.890
We insisted on it, and I'm glad we did.

01:07:06.956 --> 01:07:08.625
SO NICE

01:07:08.691 --> 01:07:09.759
I'm happy right now.

01:07:12.529 --> 01:07:13.530
[man] Jimin's buying.

01:07:14.664 --> 01:07:16.466
THUMBS UP

01:07:16.533 --> 01:07:17.967
We made you come here.

01:07:18.034 --> 01:07:22.071
It wasn't even on today's schedule.
We were supposed to rest.

01:07:23.873 --> 01:07:25.575
We're supposed to play a game, right?

01:07:25.642 --> 01:07:27.010
A GAME WAS SCHEDULED TONIGHT

01:07:27.076 --> 01:07:28.344
Who cares about the game?

01:07:29.012 --> 01:07:30.713
We should. We need an allowance.

01:07:30.780 --> 01:07:32.849
-[man] You must do it tomorrow.
-Of course.

01:07:32.916 --> 01:07:35.852
AT THE COUNTER

01:07:41.357 --> 01:07:43.927
JUST ONE TAP, AND THE PAYMENT GOES THROUGH

01:07:43.993 --> 01:07:45.161
HANYA KETIK

01:07:45.695 --> 01:07:46.796
Inilah kehidupan moden.

01:07:49.399 --> 01:07:51.901
PARK JIMIN FLEX

01:07:56.439 --> 01:08:01.210
PETANG YANG MENYEMBUNYIKAN DARI AWAL HINGGA AKHIR

01:08:02.679 --> 01:08:04.781
TEPUKAN! LELAKI HEBAT PARK JIMIN

01:08:07.016 --> 01:08:08.251
Terima kasih, semua!

01:08:08.318 --> 01:08:10.219
PETANG DI MANA SEMUA ORANG GEMBIRA

01:08:10.753 --> 01:08:12.021
[kedua-duanya ketawa]

01:08:12.088 --> 01:08:16.259
SEPERTI PENGAKHIR FILEM BELIA

01:08:22.498 --> 01:08:24.534
-[Jimin] Selamat malam.
-[Jung Kook] Selamat malam!

01:08:25.868 --> 01:08:29.272
MEMERIKSA PENAMPILANNYA DI DALAM KAMERA
SEBELUM TIDUR

01:08:37.113 --> 01:08:38.915
Anda akan melihatnya di skrin,

01:08:38.982 --> 01:08:42.685
tapi bila saya tengok kamera kat sini,

01:08:42.752 --> 01:08:46.189
ia mengekori mata dan muka saya.

01:08:46.255 --> 01:08:47.824
PANDANGAN KAMERA JIMIN SEDANG MELIHAT

01:08:47.890 --> 01:08:48.891
SERONOK, KAN?

01:08:51.394 --> 01:08:53.563
JIMIN BERJALAN DENGAN JARI UNTUK MENCUCI MULUT

01:08:53.630 --> 01:08:56.165
JIMIN KELUAR, JUNG KOOK MASUK

01:08:57.166 --> 01:09:02.171
DI MANA IA?

01:09:07.610 --> 01:09:08.678
DI SANA IA ADA

01:09:09.579 --> 01:09:14.584
PAJAMA YANG DIJUMPAI TERSEMBUNYI DI ANTARA BANTAL

01:09:17.420 --> 01:09:22.425
JUNG KOOK BERPAJAM

01:09:24.360 --> 01:09:25.528
JIMIN JUGA DAH BERSEDIA UNTUK TIDUR

01:09:25.595 --> 01:09:27.296
MASA HIDRASI +1

01:09:28.698 --> 01:09:30.133
MASA HIDRASI +2

01:09:33.369 --> 01:09:36.105
GEGAR

01:09:38.408 --> 01:09:40.643
FWOOSH

01:09:41.244 --> 01:09:44.280
URUT

01:09:47.250 --> 01:09:51.487
URUT KAKI

01:09:55.725 --> 01:09:59.996
BERPUAS HATI

01:10:01.097 --> 01:10:02.965
MASA UNTUK TIDUR

01:10:03.466 --> 01:10:07.970
ZZZ...

01:10:09.205 --> 01:10:10.740
Jom tidur.

01:10:10.807 --> 01:10:13.009
Hari ini merupakan hari yang panjang dan meletihkan.

01:10:15.411 --> 01:10:16.412
Adakah ini dia?

01:10:17.847 --> 01:10:20.283
Tuhan, tiada apa yang berlaku mengikut kehendakku.

01:10:24.320 --> 01:10:25.688
Awak pergi ke sana.

01:10:28.958 --> 01:10:30.259
Dan awak di sini.

01:10:30.793 --> 01:10:35.531
MASUK KE KATIL, POSISI YANG SEMPURNA

01:10:43.206 --> 01:10:44.841
Saya kena set alarm.

01:10:48.211 --> 01:10:52.982
PENGGERA DISET UNTUK 7:20

01:10:53.049 --> 01:10:55.651
PENGGERA DISET UNTUK 7:15

01:10:55.718 --> 01:10:58.688
PENGGERA DISET UNTUK 7:25

01:10:59.422 --> 01:11:00.490
