-Okey, okay.

01:27:44.025 --> 01:27:46.228
KEMAHIRAN TERUNGGUL DIBONGKAR

01:27:46.294 --> 01:27:48.396
INGIN TAHU

01:27:49.131 --> 01:27:50.432
Baiklah, kita mulakan.

01:27:50.499 --> 01:27:51.933
Cham Cham Cham.

01:27:52.000 --> 01:27:53.001
LANGKAH YANG DIGILAS DENGAN BAIK

01:27:53.068 --> 01:27:54.636
-30 minit.
-[dalam Bahasa Inggeris] Ayuh.

01:27:54.703 --> 01:27:55.704
Giliran awak, Jung Kook.

01:27:55.771 --> 01:27:57.305
Angkat mata anda seperti ini.

01:27:57.372 --> 01:27:59.040
JUNG KOOK CUBA KEMAHIRAN

01:27:59.107 --> 01:28:01.042
